Hello Atto,

Peak season is just around the corner, and being prepared can make all the difference. Our recent webinar, “A Masterclass on Feed Optimisation and Peak Readiness”, is now available to watch on demand.

This session is packed with practical insights to help you optimise feeds, leverage performance intelligence, and maximise results.

Here’s a snapshot of what you’ll learn:

- How to identify and fix Google Merchant Center disapprovals early to keep feeds healthy and complete.
- How AI-driven feed enrichment and automated product classification improve visibility and ROAS.
- The power of our Feed Management and Advertising Channel solutions, combining Google Ads and feed data to spot opportunities, test content, and drive measurable results.
- Customer success stories, including a 314% ROAS increase and 275% growth in conversion rates.

Don’t miss these proven strategies to make this peak season your most successful yet.

Watch the Webinar On Demand
